high_descs: Walk towards the black desk, then turn left and walk over to the small end table.
Pick up the rightmost mug off of the end table.
Turn right to face the black desk.
Put the mug on the desk to the left of the tissue box.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and look down.
Pick up the mug off of the small end table.
Turn right and take a step forward, then look down at the desk.
Put the mug on the desk behind the pen.

high_descs: Move towards the desk, then turn left to face the small black cabinet.
Pick up the mug on the your right.
Turn right to face the desk.
Place the mug on the desk between the pen and box of tissue.
Turn left to face the small black cabinet again.
Pick up the remaining mug from the top of the cabinet.
Turn right to face the desk again.
Place the mug on the desk between the pen and lamp.

high_descs: Take two steps forward and turn left to face a small cabinet with two cups on its top
Pick up the cup on the right side
Turn to your right to face the office-table
Put the cup on the office-table
Go back to the small cabinet
Pick the cup up from the top of the cabinet
Turn to your right to face the office-table
Put the cup to the left of the first cup on the table
